Record Class ViewEvaluationContext

au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.context.ViewEvaluationContext

All Implemented Interfaces:
EvaluationContext
public record ViewEvaluationContext(@Nonnull FhirPathContext fhirPathContext, @Nonnull FunctionRegistry functionRegistry, @Nonnull ResourceResolver resourceResolver) extends Record implements EvaluationContext

An implementation of EvaluationContext used for evaluating FHIRPath expressions within FHIR views.

This class combines three key components needed for FHIRPath evaluation:

  • A FhirPathContext that provides access to variables and the input context
  • A FunctionRegistry that provides access to FHIRPath functions
  • A ResourceResolver that provides access to FHIR resources
